'''子实层'''（{{lang|en|hymenium}}），是[[子囊菌門|子囊菌門]]與[[擔子菌門|擔子菌門]][[真菌|真菌]][[子實層體|子實層體]]上的構造。[[子实体_(真菌)|子實體]]中，最內側的組織為[[菌髓|菌髓]]，其外為子實下層（subhymenium），最外側即為子實層<ref name= tata>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4fcGAZBbZHAC&pg=PA250&lpg=PA250&dq=hymenium+subhymenium&source=bl&ots=MJ6z0dqg_N&sig=jJaYk7pQW_rNvNvFHRrRTWoCppI&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwinsrKK_bPdAhUeJTQIHfQ2DC04ChDoATAAegQIABAB#v=onepage&q=hymenium%20subhymenium&f=false|title=Textbook of Fungi|author=O.P. Sharma|publisher=Tata McGraw-Hill Education|year=1989|isbn=0074603299|page=251|access-date=2018-09-11|archive-date=2021-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210706040314/https://books.google.com/books?id=4fcGAZBbZHAC&pg=PA250&lpg=PA250&dq=hymenium+subhymenium&source=bl&ots=MJ6z0dqg_N&sig=jJaYk7pQW_rNvNvFHRrRTWoCppI&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwinsrKK_bPdAhUeJTQIHfQ2DC04ChDoATAAegQIABAB#v=onepage&q=hymenium%20subhymenium&f=false}}</ref>。子實層的部分細胞可發育成{{link-en|担子|basidium}}或[[子囊|子囊]]，並產生有性孢子，其他細胞則發育成{{link-en|侧丝|paraphyses}}（子囊菌）或{{link-en|囊状体|cystidia}}（担子菌）等非生殖細胞，提供支持、保護等功能<ref name= tata/>，側絲與囊狀體在蕈類的種類鑑別上相當重要，其形狀、細胞核數量與{{tsl|en|sepat|隔膜 (真菌)|隔膜}}的有無是某些菌类的分類依據<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mt69BwAAQBAJ&pg=PA44&dq=fungi+paraphyses+taxonomy+character&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiXrZf0_7PdAhV2JTQIHQNoDjgQ6AEIPzAD#v=onepage&q=fungi%20paraphyses%20taxonomy%20character&f=false|page=44|title=Systematics and Evolution|author=David J. McLaughlin, Joseph W. Spatafora|publisher=Springer|year=2015|isbn=3662460114|access-date=2018-09-11|archive-date=2021-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210809075632/https://books.google.com/books?id=mt69BwAAQBAJ&pg=PA44&dq=fungi+paraphyses+taxonomy+character&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiXrZf0_7PdAhV2JTQIHQNoDjgQ6AEIPzAD#v=onepage&q=fungi%20paraphyses%20taxonomy%20character&f=false}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?hl=zh-TW&id=p09FAQAAIAAJ&dq=fungi+cystidia+taxonomy+character&focus=searchwithinvolume&q=cystidia|page=135|title=The Mycota: A Comprehensive Treatise on Fungi as Experimental Systems for Basic and Applied Research|volume=7|author=Karl Esser, Paul A. Lemke|publisher=Springer-Verlag|year=2001|isbn=0387580034|access-date=2018-09-11|archive-date=2021-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210809075612/https://books.google.com/books?hl=zh-TW&id=p09FAQAAIAAJ&dq=fungi+cystidia+taxonomy+character&focus=searchwithinvolume&q=cystidia}}</ref>。

以下為一些[[担子菌门|担子菌门]]與[[子囊菌门|子囊菌门]]真菌的子實層形態。

* {{link-en|伞菌|agaric}}的子实层位於其[[菌褶|菌褶]]的垂直面。
* [[牛肝菌|牛肝菌]]的子实层位於海绵质的構造上。
* [[尘菌|尘菌]]的子实层位於内部。
* [[鬼笔菌|鬼笔菌]]的子实层位於内部，呈现时伴有恶臭的胶体。
* [[盘菌|盘菌]]的子实层位於盘状子實體的内弧面。
* [[猴头菇|猴头菌]]的子實層位於齒狀構造的外側。

